{"tid":969366,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人版恐懼鬥室］波蘭「密室逃脫」遊戲場地火警　5少女慶生命喪災場","createTime":"2019-01-05T04:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T06:35:10.000Z","uid":187033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8481ef24c0fc56e0ebb992d936533e27aad512db","tid":969366,"uid":187033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"火警於當地時間約下午5時發生。消防員撲熄大火後，在現場發現5名15歲死者。當局相信事發時一班朋友正為其中一人慶祝生日。<br />\n<br />\n消防部門發言人庫比亞克（Tomasz Kubiak）稱，5名死者所在房間未有直接被大火波及，但鄰近起火地點。波蘭國營通訊社PAP報道指，有傳死者死於吸入過量一氧化碳。<br />\n<br />\n意外亦導致一名25歲男子燒傷。傷者目前於深切治療部留醫，未能接受警方問話。<br />\n<br />\n總統杜達（Andrzej Duda）形容為非常嚴重的悲劇，當地市長宣布周日（6日）全市為意外哀悼。內政部長布魯津斯基（Joachim Brudzinski）亦下令嚴查全國「密室逃脫」遊戲場地的消防設施。<br />\n<br />\n「密室逃脫」遊戲的玩家會被鎖在房間或建築物內，必須找尋線索逃出密室。遊戲廣受波蘭青少年歡迎，全國有超過1000個同類遊戲場地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/279039/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD-%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%E9%80%83%E8%84%AB-%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6-5%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%85%B6%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%96%AA%E7%81%BD%E5%A0%B4?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F279039%2F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD-%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E9%2580%2583%25E8%2584%25AB-%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6-5%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2596%25AA%25E7%2581%25BD%25E5%25A0%25B4%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=%2FeKTHZEMV7CeDJoLvyKtooM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=b165533a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/279039/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD-%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%E9%80%83%E8%84%AB-%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6-5%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%85%B6%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%96%AA%E7%81%BD%E5%A0%B4?utm_medium=So